es to unreliable sources where they are used inappropriately june  learn how and when to remove this template message this articles factual accuracy is disputed relevant discussion may be found on the talk page please help to ensure that disputed statements are reliably sourced august  learn how and when to remove this template message learn how and when to remove this template message the sovereign military order of the temple of jerusalem latin ordo supremus militaris templi hierosolymitani osmth is a selfstyled order and international ngo osmth is often referred to as knights templar international osmthkti osmth does not officially recognize the claims laid out in the larmenius charter as historically valid but makes a moral and ethical claim to follow in the same spiritual path as the original order of the knights templar osmth which is open to christians of any denomination operates as a charity and engages in diplomatic and humanitarian works contents  history  organisation  sovereign military order of the temple of jerusalem smotj  ordre souverain et militaire du temple de jérusalem osmtj  references  further reading  external links historyedit the selfstyled lordre du temple founded in france in  claimed to be the continuation of the medieval knights templar using the larmenius charter as evidence of its pedigree the order was officially reconstituted in  by bernardraymond fabrépalaprat  and recognized as an order of chivalry by its patron napoleon bonaparte in  in  antonio campello pinto de sousa fontes  claimed that the osmth was the continuation of lordre du temple fernando campello pinto pereira de sousa fontes succeeded his father as the head of the order in   in  a split occurred within the osmth when general antoine originally antoni zdrojewski was unexpectedly elected as the new grand master of the osmth at the convent of paris in september  zdrojewski became the head of one faction of the order which he referred to by the french translation ordre souverain et militaire du temple de jérusalem osmtj those loyal to fernando de sousa fontes continued to be referred to by the latin translation ordo supremus militaris templi hierosolymitani osmth in  osmth voted to expel fernando de sousa fonte from the order this resulted in another schism with those loyal to fernando de sousa fonte forming a new organization presently known as osmthregency while the remainder of the organization continued on as osmth now known as osmthkti ordo supremus militaris templi hierosolymitani  knights templar international while osmthktis rituals and traditions are currently based upon those of the historical knights templar according to its website and their present leader grand master patrick rea there is no direct historical lineage claimed by osmth between osmth and the th century templars in  the order was accredited by the united nations economic and social council as a nongovernmental organisation in special consultative status one of over  organizations to hold this status the order is an associate member of the international peace bureau and an affiliate of the international center for religion  diplomacy which was founded by one of osmths members in  osmth was elected as a board member of congo conference of ngos in consultative status with the united nationscitation needed organisationedit the order exists in each country under different jurisdictions in america the order is known as the sovereign military order of the temple of jerusalem inc this being the english rendering of the latin name they should not be confused with a multitude of other selfstyled knights templar or the masonic knights templar osmth is registered in geneva swiss reg no ch and is in special consultative status with the economic and social council of the united nations has over  active members in austria bulgaria canada croatia england  wales finland france germany greece ireland italy mexico norway portugal scotland serbia and in the united states osmth operates in a number of countries providing humanitarian aid  such as the river jordan project that is supported by hm king abdullah of jordan the ecumenical organization operates as a modernday network of educated professionals as of august  the organization had approximately  members christian men who join the organisation are selfstyled as knights with the title of chevalier and females are termed dames with the title of chevaleresse or chevalière the modern order claims over  members allegedly including leaders in the military business government and ecclesiastical communities the royal patron of the osmth is hh princess elizabeth of ysenburgbüdingenwachtersbach b  she is the widow of hsh prince ferdinand heinrich of ysenburgbüdingenwachtersbach and the eldest daughter of prince friedrich ferdinand of schleswigholsteinsonderburgglücksburg   sovereign military order of the temple of jerusalem smotjedit the sovereign military order of the temple of jerusalem smotj is an american autonomous grand priory of the ordo supremus militaris templi hierosolymitani osmth branch of the ordo supremus militaris templi hierosolymitani this name sovereign military order of the temple of jerusalem smotj has been trademarked and is used exclusively in america by the smotj and thus does not refer to the group of organizations tracing lineage to osmth but rather to the current osmth only ordre souverain et militaire du temple de jérusalem osmtjedit as mentioned in history osmtj was formed by a faction of osmth in  it was headed by general antoine originally antoni zdrojewski  until his death in  zdrojewski was succeeded by george lamirand as the new head of the osmtj until his death in  george lamirand was succeeded by dr nicolas haimovici hastier who is the current osmtj grand master today referencesedit  a b osmth templar legacy page osmthorg retrieved    thomas brian templar legacy osmthorg retrieved    a b osmth brochure p    pdf osmthorg retrieved    a b dead link  osmth histo