ki  until his death in  zdrojewski was succeeded by george lamirand as the new head of the osmtj until his death in  george lamirand was succeeded by dr nicolas haimovici hastier who is the current osmtj grand master today referencesedit  a b osmth templar legacy page osmthorg retrieved    thomas brian templar legacy osmthorg retrieved    a b osmth brochure p    pdf osmthorg retrieved    a b dead link  osmth history and goals of the contemporary templar order osmthorg retrieved    sovereign military order of the temple of jerusalem pdf osmthorg retrieved    a b chronologie raymond bernard  amorc  mouvements templiers fghochecom retrieved    religious movements  neotemplarism religious movement whatwhenhowcom retrieved    james r lewis the order of the solar temple the temple of death page  ashgate publishing limited  isbn   real knights templar are philanthropists readingeaglecom retrieved    outreachunorgngorelations unorg retrieved    wayback machine  march  archived from the original on    ordo supremus militaris templi hierosolymitani osmthorg retrieved    christopher hodapp alice von kannon the templar code for dummies pages  wiley publishing inc  isbn   watson kathy humanitarian projects wwwosmthorg   watson kathy jordan river project wwwosmthorg   a b smotj about us page smotjorg retrieved    real knights templar are philanthropists readingeaglecom retrieved    osmth knights manual pdf osmthorg p  retrieved    thomas brian modern order osmthorg retrieved    thomas brian royal patron osmthorg retrieved    smotj about us page international section smotjorg retrieved    osmth list of priories osmthorg retrieved    modern order theknightstemplarorg retrieved    ordre souverain et militaire du temple de jérusalem osmtj – modern order osmtjnet retrieved   further readingedit bbc website what are the knights templar up to now news magazine  bbc radio  on the trail of the templars program audio first broadcast  stephen howarth the knights templar  isbn  chev leo thys